此时培训班已经发生 1 传 5 疫情。这 5 人系通化市源升品质生活坊的负责人（男，37 岁）和 4 名员工。 北京日报客户端记者注意到，加上今天公主岭市和通化市通报新增的 62 例无症状感染者，此次超级传播事件已经导致 3 市 81 人感染，分布在通化市（61 例）、公主岭市（19 例）、松原市（1 例）。 据吉林省卫健委 1 月 13 日通报，全省新增无症状感染者 7 例，其中 3 例为黑龙江省输入无症状感染者，4 例为关联无症状感染者。此次通报中的该名无症状感染者 3，就是后续导致了吉林多地多人感染的超级传播者。1 传 81！吉林省超级传播事件持续，传播链条一文读懂"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-4dc0b7bb08398117d900ff0e1e28475e_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "280 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/439640554"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I1oKlns6jyLExEAMaCDU5OTc1OTg4IKj3iYAGMAI4nANAB3IJNDM5NjQwNTU0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "8_1610831877.3552113", "card_id": "Q_439488842", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 100}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待 2021 年 1 月 15 日基金大跌？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-2a97cd9719751afb61220aea4d0d68db_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "276 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/439488842"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I1oKlns6jyLExEAMaCDU5OTQyMjgyILTkhIAGMAk46ANACHIJNDM5NDg4ODQyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "9_1610831877.3554773", "card_id": "Q_437497000", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 151}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "各位拿到小米 11 的兄弟们，体验过后感觉咋样？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "续航，发热等方面有没有什么严重的问题？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-4ff174ed0be572be95b58a67dc56f179_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "258 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/437497000"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I1oKlns6jyLExEAMaCDU5NTAwMzIxIIeDv/8FMAY47gJACXIJNDM3NDk3MDAweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_li